# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# <type>(<scope>): <subject>  ← max 100 characters, imperative, no period
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Type examples:
#   feat     → new feature
#   fix      → bug fix
#   refactor → refactoring without functional changes
#   style    → formatting, spaces, commas (no logical changes)
#   test     → add or modify tests
#   docs     → documentation only
#   chore    → build, dependencies, config (nothing touching src or test)
#   perf     → performance improvement
#   ci       → CI/CD pipeline changes
#   revert   → revert a previous commit
#   wip      → work in progress
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Message body (optional) — explain the WHY, not the WHAT
# Leave a blank line between subject and body.
# Wrap at 72 characters.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Footer (optional)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Breaking change:  BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
# Issue reference:  Refs #456
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
